snippet.title: Johnny and Amber's Compatibility Assessed
snippet.description:
Thank you for stopping by my channel. The Real Soulmate Formula is a product  that makes assessments of relationships between couples, friends and families. It is in search of those  relationships that are or have the potential to be happy, harmonious and healthy.  The Real Soulmate Formula has been used to assess over 4000 relationships and it is 95% accurate. There are 5 compatibility questions and 10 life conditioning questions. A happy, harmonious and healthy relationship is discovered when a couple has 3 to 5 matching answers out of 5 compatibility questions.  The Real Soulmate Formula is matchmaking made easy.  Thank you for watching.
